Reader
=====

Reader is a fun little rss reader with some social features. This is the primary codebase for [http://1kpl.us/](http://1kpl.us/)

Setup
=====

**Requirements**

  1. Ruby 2.0.0 (MRI)
  2. Bundler (gem install bundler)
  3. PostgreSQL 9+

To setup the app just type (ignore the `$`):

``` bash
$ script/setup
```

